lenders.name: Corinne and family
lenders.loan_because: I believe that all people should have as much control as possible over their own lives. Too many who live in disadvantaged countries have had their lives torn apart because of the policies of the IFIs and WTO, the complacency of UN member countries,  and corporate and government corruption. As Mohammad Yunus has said, the problem is complex, the solution is simple. I cannot change the deeply entrenched, institutionalized and systemic problems - which need to be completely shifted - but I can help another women care for her family.
lenders.occupational_info: I teach sociology at our university. One course I often teach is called "Social Control and Social Justice". I introduce students to the World Bank, IMF,  and WTO and get them to understand the injustices put on developing countries. I then introduce them to the UN and NGOs - and show them the thousands that operate in Africa. We discuss the problems NGOs face and students compare their structure to the WB and IMF. Then, I introduce them to micro-financing, starting, of course, with Mohammad Yunus's Grameen. Then, I show them Kiva. They become VERY excited. They must choose a business that they would help if they could. They have to look up where they live and find out if the WB or IMF have implimented SAPs in that country - and if there are NGOs working in the country. They really get excited.

Wine guy, host of Wine Library TV. Video blogger and Businessman that loves people and the hustle.

Gary Vaynerchuk has captured attention with his pioneering, multi-faceted approach to personal branding and business. After primarily utilizing traditional advertising techniques to build his family’s local retail wine business into a national industry leader, Gary rapidly leveraged social media tools such as Twitter and Facebook to promote Wine Library TV, his video blog about wine. Gary has always had an early to market approach launching Wine Library’s retail website in 1997 and Wine Library TV in February of 2006. Gary’s success has led to a 7-figure book deal, several national TV appearances, and a flurry of speaking engagements around the world.
